    "description": "本課程介紹人工智慧的發展與應用，教導學生認識人工智慧的技術與瞭解人工智慧開發的方法。本課程是以設計思考與問題導向的人工智慧技術應用之課程，學生將學習從生活周遭發覺有價值之應用題目，並透過課堂討論與分享期末專案。<br>This course introduces the development and application of artificial intelligence, helps students to understand the technology of artificial intelligence and the development methods. This course is a design thinking and problem-oriented application of artificial intelligence technology. Students will discover valuable application topics in daily life and share their final projects through classroom discussions.",
